Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Female' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select any Examination radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Yes' radio button from 'Contrast enhanced' box from Page 03 of Pelvic MRI
And I go to Page 09 of Pelvic MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Urinary bladder wall thickening' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled

And 'Artifacts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Not sufficient bladder filling' checkbox is enabled

And 'Inserted bladder catheter' checkbox is enabled
And 'Double-j catheter right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Double-j catheter left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Characterization I' tab
Then 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled

And 'Max. expansion ' input field is enabled
And '2nd plane' input field is enabled
And '3rd plane' input field is enabled

And 'Strong' radio button is enabled
And 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'No' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Focal' radio button
Then 'Base of the bladder' checkbox is enabled
And 'Right lateral wall' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left lateral wall' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bladder neck' checkbox is enabled
And 'Trigonum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Roof of bladder' checkbox is enabled
And 'Anterior wall' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior wall' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Strong' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Heterogeneous' radio button
Then 'Central' radio button is enabled
And 'Peripheral' radio button is enabled
And 'Marginal' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Low' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Heterogeneous' radio button
Then 'Central' radio button is enabled
And 'Peripheral' radio button is enabled
And 'Marginal' radio button is enabled
